 | [[Centrism|Center]]{{refn|
* {{Cite news|url=https://fivethirtyeight.com/features/the-six-wings-of-the-democratic-party/|title=The Six Wings Of The Democratic Party|first=Perry Jr.|last=Bacon|work=[[FiveThirtyEight]]|date=March 11, 2019|access-date=October 21, 2021|archive-date=August 15, 2021|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210815092648/https://fivethirtyeight.com/features/the-six-wings-of-the-democratic-party/|url-status=live}}
