* {{cite book|last1=Alterman|first1=Eric|title=Why We're Liberals: A Political Handbook for Post-Bush America|date=2008|publisher=Penguin|isbn=9780670018604|page=339|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=mhO41uVWOQIC&q=huge+swing+away+from+the+center&pg=PA339|accessdate=March 13, 2017|quote=Suffice to say that there has not been a huge swing away from the center since the 1970s.}}
